  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pedro Land DX is a compilation of short adventures, starring a man named Pedro Sombrero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump, and shoot your way to victory in the game's retro-hard campaigns, uncover secrets, and become a true gunman!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pedro Land DX involves run-and-gun action platforming like beloved games of the late 80s to early 90s, with a western feel!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also comes with a free manual! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pedro Land DX is a compilation of short adventures, starring a man named Pedro Sombrero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump, and shoot your way to victory in the game's retro-hard campaigns, uncover secrets, and become a true gunman!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pedro Land DX involves run-and-gun action platforming like beloved games of the late 80s to early 90s, with a western feel!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also comes with a free manual! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
